msgid "Help us spread free software!"
msgstr "Help ons vrije software te verspreiden!"

#: lib/views/link_buttons.php:22
msgid ""
"Simply copy/paste the code next to your favorite button into your website."
msgstr "Kopi&euml;er en plak de code naast je favoriete knop in je webpagina."

#: lib/views/link_buttons.php:58
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Gebruik"

#: lib/views/link_buttons.php:59
msgid ""
"We kindly ask that these buttons be used only to point to <em>get "
"GNU/Linux!</em> websites."
msgstr "We willen vriendelijk vragen deze knoppen alleen te gebruiken om naar de <em>get GNU/Linux!</em> websites te linken."

